{"tid":2208811,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩驅使人類咁鍾意用傷殘人士嘅設施？","createTime":"2020-09-19T08:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T13:39:47.000Z","uid":354255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3a902fcca1bc6f2e608c99698cdf27937995b743","tid":2208811,"uid":354255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:00:20.000Z","msg":"荃灣商場<br />\n呢個係傷殘人士車位<br />\n呢條友一張殘疾人士泊車證都冇<br />\n附近咁多車位唔泊<br />\n傷殘人士設施香d？<br />\n定係特別鍾意搭lift<br />\n同你架車拍寫真<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kh9Pzga.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkh9Pzga.jpg&h=f6bd8187&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xsjPzge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxsjPzge.jpg&h=700f074f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7y38PPC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7y38PPC.jpg&h=3b8e605d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fce3353fead503e56e4d9fa205eb4fcdaffca332","tid":2208811,"uid":363330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:06:33.000Z","msg":"因為大多數人都守紀律唔佔用<br />\n而實際上揸車嘅傷殘人士又唔多<br />\n所以個位多數都會空咗出嚟<br />\n再者傷殘人士用嘅會預多啲空間<br />\n<br />\n一啲冇咁守紀律嘅人見一個咁鬆動又空出嚟嘅位<br />\n貪方便就去用"},{"pid":"80931c3448058db7af00def9b1e5c69e3b326ed7","tid":2208811,"uid":164240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:39:51.000Z","msg":"仲以為你話coffee<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bccb4f312269d69390d75b931e758c5f53e1786","tid":2208811,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:46:01.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"2f6ce90a0cdaf03ca7360727b9635027ede23107","tid":2208811,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:47:56.000Z","msg":"如果車上有人坐輪椅係咪都唔用得？<br />\n要有證先得？"},{"pid":"3f2c547ffe3d2d8cdd0e164d9bace8ab7469c9bc","tid":2208811,"uid":354255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80931c3